# Design Policy Writing Rules

## Document Definition
- **Filename**: `outputs/docs/05-디자인정책.md`
- **Purpose**: Define design tokens, components, interaction patterns, accessibility, and Hi-fi guidance
- **Owner**: Design Lead

## Prerequisites
- `outputs/docs/04-화면설계.md` approved (Gate A)

## Strict Sequential Mode (Enforced)

This document is SECTION-GATED. Produce exactly one section per turn and wait for explicit approval before moving on.

### Hard Rules
- Only one section per turn. If asked to "전체 작성", refuse and ask which section to start.
- Use approval phrase to proceed with SECTION TITLE (not numbers).
- Keep process/gate messages in chat, not in the document.

### Per-Section Pre-Work Report (Short)
- Goal: "섹션 N 초안 작성"
- Scope: that section only
- Approach: 2-3 bullets
- Rule Applied: `.cursor/rules/05-디자인정책-규칙.mdc`

## Required Sections (Order, One per Turn)
1. 목적 & 범위
2. 토큰: 컬러
3. 토큰: 타이포그래피
4. 토큰: 간격/반경/그림자/레이어
5. 컴포넌트: 베이직(버튼/카드/텍스트/아이콘/아바타)
6. 컴포넌트: 입력류(인풋/셀렉트/체크/라디오/스위치/슬라이더)
7. 컴포넌트: 피드백/상태(스낵바/토스트/스피너/스켈레톤/오버레이)
8. 레이아웃 패턴(헤더/푸터/탭바/모달/드로어)
9. 모션 원칙(스케일/페이드/슬라이드/듀레이션)
10. 접근성(명암, 터치 타겟, 포커스 링)
11. 프로토타입(핵심 플로우 하이파이 링크)
12. 승인 기준(Gate B)

